data.meta_description: Shahrukh Khan - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Shah Rukh Khan provides an autobiographical summary of his early life in 3 paragraphs. He describes being born in New Delhi and attending St. Columba's School run by strict Irish brothers. He shares fond memories of his teachers and his favorite actress Mumtaz inspiring his interest in performance. Khan also discusses his father who was a gentle, well-educated man who treated him as a friend and had a great sense of humor, traits that Khan strives to emulate.
